{
  "stem": "15393.1",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Rozias ?] [?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Toen. ?] And his name was [?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Gabriel ?] [?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Toen, ?] the boy, who was an absolute terror, terror, if there ever was on in the kindergarten.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Nobody could cope with him, but because of his prominence, so to speak, there was nothing they could do.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They had to keep him.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And of course, I was just simply fascinated by [LAUGHS] the boy, because of the things he-- you know and that.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "He had a gang of boys.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And all I wanted to be able to-- to-- to be with them.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I was not interested in girls' toys, dolls and things.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "[SIGHS] And on one occasion, he said to me, alright, you will be able to be with us and do whatever we do, if you promise that you go home, today, and, at lunchtime, when everybody's quietly eating, you will say a word-- and he named a word, which was a nasty, nasty word-- very loudly at the table.",
      "word_count": 59
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I can't do that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "All right, so you can't be playing with us.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Finished.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "So I-- I was, of course, disheartened.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "He said, all right, I'm telling you once more.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "You will go home, and this is what you do.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "At the table, you say-- And tomorrow morning, when you come, and if I ask you, have you said it, and if you lie, I want you to know, I'll know it.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And of course, I went home, and I shivered.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And as we sat at the table and everybody was eating, and, suddenly, I would [CLAP] come out with my word.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I-- I can't.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean, it was arse, if you like, but in Polish, of course.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And that was a word, you know, children didn't use such words, you know?",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
